Record.Property: select distinct --top 10 mcg.nMasterCustomers_ID, mcg.cConversionType, mcg.cStandardXpedxValue, mcg.cStandardXpedxValueDesc, mcg.cCustomerSpecificValue, mcg.cCustomerSpecificValueDesc, mcg.cLegacyItemNumber, ccr.webmethodscustomerid FROM xpedx.dbo.customers C (NOLOCK) INNER JOIN xpedx.dbo.MasterCustomerGeneric_XREF mcg (NOLOCK) ON mcg.nMasterCustomers_id = C.nMasterCustomers_ID INNER JOIN xpedx.dbo.wm_CustomerCrossReference ccr ON mcg.nmastercustomers_id = substring(ccr.xpedxcustomerid,2,len(ccr.xpedxcustomerid)-1) INNER JOIN xpedx.dbo.CustomerLocations cl (NOLOCK) ON cl.nCustomers_id = C.nCustomers_id LEFT OUTER JOIN xpedx.dbo.CustomerDivisions CD (NOLOCK) ON C.nCustomers_Id = CD.nCustomers_ID LEFT OUTER JOIN xpedx.dbo.Divisions D (NOLOCK) ON CD.nDivisions_Id = D.nDivisions_ID INNER JOIN xpedx.dbo.LegacySystems ls (NOLOCK) ON D.nLegacySystems_id = ls.nLegacySystems_id LEFT OUTER JOIN xpedx.dbo.Brands B (NOLOCK) ON D.Brands_Id = B.Brands_Id WHERE C.lDeleted = 0 and cl.cShipToSuffix IS NULL and ls.cName = 'MAX' and mcg.cConversionType in ( 'UNSPSC' , 'UOM') and ccr.webmethodscustomerid is not null and mcg.cNG_datamigration_Flag <> 'M'

select distinct --mcg.nMasterCustomers_ID, mcg.cConversionType, mcg.cStandardXpedxValue, mcg.cStandardXpedxValueDesc, mcg.cCustomerSpecificValue, mcg.cCustomerSpecificValueDesc, mcg.cLegacyItemNumber FROM xpedx.dbo.customers C (NOLOCK) INNER JOIN xpedx.dbo.MasterCustomerGeneric_XREF mcg (NOLOCK) ON mcg.nMasterCustomers_id = C.nMasterCustomers_ID WHERE C.lDeleted = 0 and mcg.cConversionType in ( 'UNSPSC' , 'UOM') --and mcg.nMasterCustomers_id = 1084362336

UPDATE xpedx.dbo.MasterCustomerGeneric_XREF SET cNG_datamigration_Flag = ?, dMigratedTimestamp = ? WHERE nMasterCustomers_ID IN (SELECT substring(xpedxcustomerid,2,len(xpedxcustomerid)-1) FROM xpedx.dbo.wm_CustomerCrossReference WHERE WebMethodsCustomerID = ?);

SELECT DISTINCT ccr.webmethodscustomerid, mcgn.cStandardXpedxValue, mcgn.cCustomerSpecificValue FROM xpedx.dbo.MasterCustomerGeneric_XREF_NextGen mcgn INNER JOIN xpedx.dbo.wm_CustomerCrossReference ccr ON mcgn.nMasterCustomers_ID = substring(ccr.xpedxcustomerid,2,len(ccr.xpedxcustomerid)-1) ORDER BY 1,2,3
